    "uen": "202108443E",
    "description": "<p>ALBA E-Waste is Singapore’s National Producer Responsibility Scheme Operator for e-waste. As a sorting and logistics hub, we specialize in the collection, consolidation, and transfer of electronic waste to licensed recyclers for material recovery. Our mission is to support Singapore’s zero-waste goals by enabling responsible e-waste management and promoting circular economy practices.</p>\n<p><br>\nWe’re looking for passionate, self-driven individuals who want to make a real impact. If you're committed to creating a cleaner, smarter, and more sustainable world, we invite you to step up and be part of our journey.</p>",
